Install python and python-pip
$ yum install python
$ yum install python-pip

Install Ansible by using pip
$ pip install ansible

To check the ansible version
$ ansible --version

To create a user for ansible

$ useradd ansible
$ passwd ansible

echo "ansible ALL=(ALL) NOPASSWD:ALL" >> /etc/sudoers

create a ssh key to connect ansible user
$ ssh-keygen

$ ssh-copy-id localhost

